text:
This extension allows you to use academicons in your Quarto HTML documents. It provides an {{< ai >}} shortcode:

Mandatory <icon-name>:
{{< ai <icon-name> >}}
Optional <size=...>:
{{< ai <icon-name> <size=...> >}}

For example:



Shortcode
Icon




{{< ai arxiv >}}



{{< ai google-scholar >}}



{{< ai open-access >}}



{{< ai open-access size=5x >}}
